protobuf — Protocol Buffers (Cygwin port)

Upstream: https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protobuf
Version:  34.1 (C++ 7.34.1)
License:  BSD-3-Clause

Patch summary (12 files):

  src/google/protobuf/port_def.inc
      Disable PROTOBUF_ATTRIBUTE_WEAK on Cygwin. PE/COFF weak symbols
      collapse vtable dispatch, breaking descriptor self-registration.

  src/google/protobuf/compiler/plugin.cc
      Set binary mode on plugin stdin/stdout to prevent CRLF corruption
      of wire-format data.

  src/google/protobuf/compiler/command_line_interface_tester.cc
  src/google/protobuf/compiler/command_line_interface_unittest.cc
      Remove stale #if !defined(__CYGWIN__) guards left from a prior
      port attempt.

  upb/port/def.inc
      PE/COFF linker array and constructor macros for UPB mini-table
      registration. ELF uses __attribute__((section)), PE/COFF uses
      #pragma section with __declspec(allocate).

  upb/mini_table/generated_registry.c
      Use PE/COFF linker arrays for mini-table registration on Cygwin.

  src/google/protobuf/port_test.cc
  src/google/protobuf/descriptor_unittest.cc
  src/google/protobuf/wire_format_unittest.cc
  src/google/protobuf/compiler/code_generator_unittest.cc
      Platform regression tests for weak symbol, plugin binary mode,
      and descriptor registration fixes.

  src/google/protobuf/BUILD.bazel
      Add :protobuf_lite dep to port_test (needed for arenastring.h).

  src/README.md
      Cygwin build instructions.

Build notes:

  Requires abseil-cpp built with the same ABI flags:
    _GLIBCXX_USE_CXX11_ABI=1    (SSO string ABI)
    GTEST_HAS_PTHREAD=1          (GoogleTest pthread support)

  abseil-cpp must be installed at /usr/local before building protobuf.
  Use the phdye-cygwin abseil-cpp cygport or binary release.

Known limitations:

  Death tests fail due to Cygwin's fork() implementation. The full-test
  binary (monolithic test runner) aborts when a death test fork leaves
  stale temp directories. All non-death tests pass (745 tests).

Source: https://github.com/phdye-cygwin/protobuf, branch cygwin/v34.1
